Easy creation of dummy packages.

Build .spec files and packages from a ptest.repo description
into ptest.repo.d directory.
  - All packages provide: test42 (zypper -n rm test42)
  - Simple product/-release package support (see prodtest.repo)
  - allScripts: All triggers refer to /tmp/ptest.repo.triggers/
  - allScripts: If a file /tmp/ptest.repo.errors/%name-%version-%release.{script}
                exists, the script execution fails.

